InstalledItem.Name: CF-337 Panther Repeater
InstalledItem.Description:
Manufacturer: Klaus & Werner
Item Type: Laser Repeater
Size: 3

The CF-337 Panther is the size three model in Klaus & Werner's laser repeater line. The Panther is a true fire-and-forget weapon with a respectable power consumption-to-damage ratio. Pilots who outfit their ships with Panthers rarely regret the decision.

InstalledItem.Name: BlastChill
InstalledItem.Description:
Item Type: Cooler
Manufacturer: Lightning Power Ltd. 
Size: 1
Grade: D
Class: Civilian

The BlastChill is a consumer-grade cooler from Lightning Power Ltd. It keeps your ship running without straining its signature, but is best known for a much mocked 2945 ad campaign that promised it was Built to bring the chill.

InstalledItem.Name: LightBlossom
InstalledItem.Description:
Item Type: Power Plant
Manufacturer: Sakura Sun
Size: 1
Grade: C
Class: Civilian

Featuring stylish design and strong performance, the LightBlossom is a worthy addition to Sakura Suns line-up, continuing the reputation the conglomerate has for making everything and making it well.

InstalledItem.Name: FoxFire
InstalledItem.Description:
Item Type: Quantum Drive
Manufacturer: Ace Astrogation
Size: 1
Grade: B
Class: Competition

The FoxFire won't leave a burning trail in your wake, but this quantum drives strong performance leaves an equal impression. Making it another elegant and powerful component from the folks at Ace Astrogation.

InstalledItem.Name: Ecouter
InstalledItem.Description:
Item Type: Radar
Manufacturer: GNP
Size: 1
Grade: C
Class: Military

Space is vast and unknowable, thats why discerning pilots rely on the Ecouter small radar from GNP to keep them in the know about whats around them.

InstalledItem.Name: HEX
InstalledItem.Description:
Item Type: Shield Generator
Manufacturer: Seal Corporation
Size: 1
Grade: B
Class: Civilian

Prepare your ship for any circumstance by installing a HEX from Seal Corporation. Balanced performance and durability make this an ideal, versatile choice for those who dont know where their next adventure may take them.
